{
  "title": "Personalized or Problematic:",
  "body": "<html><body><div id=\"block-ti-west-content\">\n<article>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--type--text--bleed paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div><div class=\"hero__container hero__container--small hero__container--no-image\" data-hero-container=\"\"><div class=\"container container--max-width\"><div class=\"hero__text-container hero__text-container--center hero__text-container__small\"><h1 class=\"u-font-family-secondary hero__title\">Personalized or Problematic:<br/>Exploring the New Age of Insurance Pricing</h1></div></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div><p>Emerging data-driven technologies are revolutionizing how insurers assess and price risk. Explore how telematics, wearables, and AI-powered analytics are redefining risk pooling and raising complex ethical, regulatory, and social questions. Learn how personalization impacts fairness and accessibility, uncover strategies for maintaining transparency and trust, and review how insurers and regulators worldwide are adapting. From the “black box” problem to the call for algorithmic accountability, participants will examine where technology enhances value—and where it challenges the very principles of shared protection. </p><table style=\"font-size:inherit;margin:32px 0;width:100%;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding-right:40px;vertical-align:top;\"><strong>Pricing</strong><br/>$64.00*</td><td style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><strong>Webinar Duration</strong><br/>60 minutes</td><td style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><strong>CE Requirements</strong><br/><a href=\"https://web.theinstitutes.org/ceu/state-requirements\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Verify your state and license CE requirements</a></td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text