t__container\"><div class=\"detail-list__item\"><dt class=\"detail-list__title\"><p>Topics</p></dt><dd class=\"detail-list__desc\"><ul><li>Explore how data sources like telematics and IoT devices are reshaping traditional pricing</li><li>Examine ethical and legal risks linked to hyperpersonalized models</li><li>Understand the role of regulators in promoting fairness and transparency</li><li>Learn strategies to rebuild consumer trust and mitigate bias</li><li>Evaluate global and alternative approaches to balancing equity and innovation </li></ul></dd></div></dl></div></article></div></div></div></div></section></div></div></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div><div style=\"margin:0 auto;max-width:1200px;text-align:center;\"><h3 style=\"margin-bottom:15px;\">Choose Your Date and Time</h3><div id=\"webinar-buttons\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:16px;justify-content:center;\"><a class=\"btn btn--primary\" data-date=\"2026-03-10\" href=\"/ceu/webinars/personalized-or-problematic-exploring-new-age-insurance-pricing-20260310\" style=\"flex:1 1 calc(33.333% - 16px);max-width:360px;min-width:260px;text-align:center;\">Tue, March 10 – 1:00 PM EST</a> <a class=\"btn btn--primary\" data-date=\"2026-04-01\" href=\"/ceu/webinars/personalized-or-problematic-exploring-new-age-insurance-pricing-20260401\" style=\"flex:1 1 calc(33.333% - 16px);max-width:360px;min-width:260px;text-align:center;\">Wed, April 1 – 1:00 PM EST</a> <a class=\"btn btn--primary\" data-date=\"2026-04-30\" href=\"/ceu/webinars/personalized-or-problematic-exploring-new-age-insurance-pricing-20260430\" style=\"flex:1 1 calc(33.333% - 16px);max-width:360px;min-width:260px;text-align:center;\">Thu, April 30 – 11:00 AM EST</a></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div><secti